<% content_for :title, "About Us - Sustainable Catering Supplies | Afida" %>

<% content_for :meta_description, "Learn about Afida's commitment to providing eco-friendly catering supplies. From humble beginnings to sustainable solutions for businesses across the UK." %>

<div class="pattern-bg-grey pattern-visible">
<!-- Section 1: Hero -->
<section class="w-screen relative left-[50%] right-[50%] -mx-[50vw] overflow-hidden">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12 lg:py-16 text-center">
    <h1 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold mb-4">Our Story</h1>
    <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 max-w-2xl mx-auto">From living room beginnings to leading eco-friendly innovation</p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Section 2: Timeline -->
<section class="py-8 lg:py-12">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto relative">

      <!-- Vertical connecting line -->
      <div class="absolute left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 top-8 bottom-8 w-0.5 border-l-2 border-dashed border-black hidden md:block"></div>

      <!-- Chapter 1: The Problem -->
      <div class="relative mb-8">
        <div class="flex justify-center mb-4">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#ffb7c5] border-2 border-black rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-lg z-10">
            1
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-[#ffb7c5] border-2 border-black p-6 lg:p-8
                    shadow-[4px_4px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)]">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">The Problem</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-800 leading-relaxed">
            It all started in the aftermath of lockdown, when Marco Bungish had one simple but powerful idea: there had to be a better alternative to those soggy, short-lived paper straws.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Chapter 2: The Discovery -->
      <div class="relative mb-8">
        <div class="flex justify-center mb-4">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#79ebc0] border-2 border-black rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-lg z-10">
            2
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-[#79ebc0] border-2 border-black p-6 lg:p-8
                    shadow-[4px_4px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)]">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">The Discovery</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-800 leading-relaxed">
            After rounds of testing and debates, Marco stumbled upon a game-changing solution — a straw made from bamboo pulp. Stronger, longer-lasting, and 100% eco-friendly. It was everything the paper straw wasn't.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Chapter 3: The Launch -->
      <div class="relative mb-8">
        <div class="flex justify-center mb-4">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#fef08a] border-2 border-black rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-lg z-10">
            3
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-[#fef08a] border-2 border-black p-6 lg:p-8
                    shadow-[4px_4px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)]">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">The Launch</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-800 leading-relaxed">
            Marco teamed up with his lifelong friend Tariq, and together they launched B&B Eco — from the most humble of HQs: Tariq's living room. Armed with passion and a box full of bamboo straws, they hit the ground running. The response? Overwhelming.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Chapter 4: Today -->
      <div class="relative">
        <div class="flex justify-center mb-4">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#c4b5fd] border-2 border-black rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-lg z-10">
            4
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-[#c4b5fd] border-2 border-black p-6 lg:p-8
                    shadow-[4px_4px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)]">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Today</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-800 leading-relaxed">
            Fast forward four years, and B&B Eco has grown into Afida — now proudly supplying sustainable packaging to hundreds of businesses, from independent cafés to global names like The Ritz, Marriott, and Hawksmoor.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Section 3: Closing Tagline -->
<section class="py-8 lg:py-12">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 text-center">
    <p class="text-xl lg:text-2xl font-medium text-gray-700 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      We're here to help you ditch the plastic without compromising on quality, style, or performance.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Section 4: Client Logos -->
<%= render "pages/partials/client_logos" %>
</div>